These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
House: townhouse, cottage, tower, palace
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
2. the cottage house is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the tower house is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the tower house##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | cottage   | palace    | townhouse    | tower |
| Sport      | volleyball | baseball | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, egyptian, canadian, turkish
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the egyptian is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
4. the egyptian is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the turkish is on the right of the malaysian##1
8. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | egyptian  | canadian    | malaysian | turkish    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, quad-bike, subway
1. the person drinking water is not the person driving the scooter##6
2. the person driving the snowmobile is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the person driving the scooter is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | quad-bike | subway | snowmobile | scooter  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, handball, ice-hockey, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the person who's sport is handball##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | handball | ice-hockey | lacrosse     | golf |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

