.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, january, july, november
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##5
3. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
4. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
5. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person drinking 7up##6
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
7. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | 7up        | milk | iced-tea | fanta |
| Transport   | november | march | january     | july   |

