.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, milk, soy-milk, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, poppy, iris, daffodil
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
2. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
6. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
8. the person drinking milk is not the person who growsdaffodil##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | milk  | 7up        | soy-milk      | tea          |
| Job        | tulip | poppy | daffodil | iris |

