.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, fisherman, lawyer, teacher
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, electronic, blues, jazz
1. the bartender is in an odd position##4
2. the fan electronic is not the teacher##6
3. the fan indie is somewhere to the right of the lawyer##5
4. the fan jazz is in an even position##4
5. the fan jazz is on the left of the fan blues##1
6. the fan jazz is the lawyer##1
7. the bartender is not the fan jazz##6
8. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the teacher##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | bartender  | lawyer | teacher    | fisherman |
| Transport   | electronic | jazz | blues | indie  |

