.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, hedgehog, rabbit
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, software-developer, engineer, manager
1. the dancer is not the owner of the ferret##6
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the manager is the manager##1
4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the manager##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is not the manager##6
6. the software-developer is not the owner of the fish##6
7. the manager is in an even position##4
8. the owner of the hedgehog is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | hedgehog | ferret        | rabbit  | fish     |
| Sport   | dancer     | manager | software-developer | engineer |

