.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, poker, scrabble
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
2. the person playing monopoly is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the person playing canasta is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person playing poker is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the person playing canasta is between the person playing monopoly and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | scrabble | monopoly      | canasta | poker   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

