3. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating peach##5
6. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating kiwi##1
7. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |       3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | juice    | iced-tea | hot-chocolate | fanta         |
| Sport      | pomegranate | kiwi | peach          | pineapple |

