.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, apricot, grey, emerald
1. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes grey##5
2. the person who likes ivory is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person who likes emerald is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the right of the person who likes apricot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | grey  | apricot      | ivory  | emerald       |

